      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a driver-focused example of the iconic S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a recently serviced double VANOS system and precise valve adjustment. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring the MacPherson strut and multi-link suspension geometry perform as intended under load. While showing honest wear consistent with a well-enjoyed enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical integrity is prioritized, featuring a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and consistent fluid intervals. A purist\u2019s specification for those who value tactile mechanical feedback and high-revving throttle response.",
